OL,3,CWales to stick to 20mph but there will
OL,4,Cbe 'adjustments', says Cabinet
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FThe is to stick to its 20mph policy,
OL,8,Fbut there will be "adjustments" to the
OL,9,Fway it is implemented, according to a
OL,10,FCabinet Secretary.
OL,12,FJeremy Miles MS, the Cabinet Secretary
OL,13,Ffor Economy, Energy and Welsh
OL,14,FLanguage, said the Welsh Government is
OL,15,F"not changing the policy," but
OL,16,Facknowledged that the "implementation
OL,17,Fof that policy has differed, sometimes
OL,18,Fquite significantly, in different
OL,19,Fparts."
