OL,3,CWales to stick to 20mph but there will
OL,4,Cbe 'adjustments', says Cabinet
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FSpeaking to BBC Wales' Politics Wales
OL,8,Fprogramme on Sunday, Mr Miles said:
OL,9,F"You'd expect some level of variation
OL,10,Fbecause Wales is geographically
OL,11,Fvaried, but there perhaps has been
OL,12,Fmore variation in similar
OL,13,Fcircumstances than you would expect.
OL,15,F"So this is about making sure the
OL,16,Fguidance, and listening to the public,
OL,17,Fand councillors, is a key part of
OL,18,Fthat, and there will be some
OL,19,Fadjustments as a consequence of that,
OL,20,Fbut that's about the implementation,
OL,21,Fnot about the policy."
