OL,3,CWales to stick to 20mph but there will
OL,4,Cbe 'adjustments', says Cabinet
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FSince September 2023, local
OL,8,Fauthorities in Wales have been obliged
OL,9,Fto set speed limits in urban and
OL,10,Fresidential areas at 20mph as a
OL,11,Fdefault, even though they can keep
OL,12,Fsome of those roads at 30mph.
OL,14,FIt comes as newly-appointed Secretary
OL,15,FKen Skates is expected to make his
OL,16,Ffirst ministerial statement on the
OL,17,FWelsh Government's transport policies
OL,18,Fin the Senedd this coming Tuesday.
