OL,3,CWales to stick to 20mph but there will
OL,4,Cbe 'adjustments', says Cabinet
OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FThe new Transport Secretary has said
OL,8,Fthat there will be changes to zones to
OL,9,Fensure that they're "truly targeted"
OL,10,Fin areas "where children and the
OL,11,Felderly are at risk."
OL,13,FSpeaking in a debate called by the
OL,14,FWelsh Conservatives to try to overturn
OL,15,Fthe 20mph policy, Mr Skates said he'll
OL,16,Fbe outlining "measures that will be
OL,17,Ftaken in coming weeks and months in
OL,18,Frelation to all matters relating to
OL,19,Ftransport and particularly to 20mph."
