OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,FThe Leader of Cardiff Council also
OL,8,Fspoke about potential changes to the
OL,9,F20mph limit on S4C's Y Byd yn ei Le
OL,10,Fthis week, saying that "half a dozen"
OL,11,F20mph roads in Cardiff could revert to
OL,12,Ftheir original speed limit.
OL,14,FLabour Councillor Huw Thomas said: "I
OL,15,Fcan say that certainly in Cardiff's
OL,16,Fcase, there will be a review. This is
OL,17,Fa policy we've been introducing in
OL,18,FCardiff over a number of years.
