OL,5,CSecretary
OL,7,Fclaim their pressure is "moving the
OL,8,Fdial among Labour Government
OL,9,FMinisters," but continue to call for
OL,10,Fthe overall policy to be scrapped.
OL,12,FNatasha Asghar MS, Welsh Conservative
OL,13,FShadow Transport Minister said: "The
OL,14,Fpeople of Wales have rightfully taken
OL,15,Fsignificant issue with Labour's 20mph
OL,16,Fpolicy and 'correcting guidance' will
OL,17,Fnot be enough to ease concerns."
OL,19,FShe said that a "more targeted
OL,20,Fapproach is needed with the support of
OL,21,Fthe Welsh people."
